name: RIVE GAUCHE POUR HOMME : LA COLLECTION
description: Rive Gauche Pour Homme evokes the assurance of the man. A state of mind, an attitude, a lifestyle. An invitation to become the man about whom all the women dream: the man Rive Gauche. A man who knows how to ally elegance, power and sensuality, with a vital, reassuring force, always marked with a small wild side.
